{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit has a style engine that makes it easy to customize the style of your keyboard. However, the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyleService","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is a bit tricky to use if you need to easily apply many different styles."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"👑 ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/KeyboardKit\/KeyboardKitPro","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" therefore unlocks a theme engine that can be used to easily style your keyboard with different styles, and provides you with many predefined themes, templates, and theme-based views. You can easily create custom themes as well.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Namespace","text":"Namespace","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit has a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme","isActive":true},{"text":" type that is also a namespace for theme-related types and views, like ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/Shelf","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/ShelfItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Context","anchor":"Context","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit has an observable "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" class that can be used to handle themes and auto-persisted "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext\/settings-swift.property","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". It also has auto-persisted "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext\/settings-swift.property","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" that can be used to persist themes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit automatically creates an instance of this class, injects it into ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardInputViewController\/state"},{"text":" and updates it whenever the theme changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Services","type":"heading","anchor":"Services"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In KeyboardKit, a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyleService\/themeBased(keyboardContext:themeContext:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" style service can be used to apply a keyboard theme:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["override func viewDidLoad() {","    super.viewDidLoad()","    setupPro(for: .myApp) { license in","        self.services.styleService = .themeBased(","            keyboardContext: state.keyboardContext,","            themeContext: state.themeContext","        )","    } ","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can inherit ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyle\/ThemeBasedStyleService","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to customize themes even further, which lets you mix the benefits of themes and styles.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Settings","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Settings"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit has a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"-specific "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/Settings"},{"text":" type with auto-persisted settings. ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext\/settings-swift.property","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is used by default within KeyboardKit."}]},{"text":"Themes","anchor":"Themes","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme"},{"text":" can provide keyboard-related styles in a way that can be easily used and modified. A theme can also define style variations that can be used to customize a constrained set of theme properties.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit Pro unlocks a bunch of themes and style variations, as well as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyle\/ThemeBasedStyleService"},{"type":"text","text":" that lets you apply themes with the style service concept that is still used by the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit Pro unlocks many standard themes, like ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/standard","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/swifty","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/minimal"},{"type":"text","text":". These themes also have style variations, that lets you vary their appearance, like the standard theme’s "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/StandardStyle\/blue","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/StandardStyle\/green","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" variations:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"standard","type":"image"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"standard-blue"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"standard-green"}]}],"size":1}],"numberOfColumns":3,"type":"row"}],"title":".standard"},{"title":".swifty","content":[{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"swifty","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"swifty-blue"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"swifty-green"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"numberOfColumns":3,"type":"row"}]},{"content":[{"numberOfColumns":3,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"minimal","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"minimal-blue"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"minimal-sunset"}]}]}],"type":"row"}],"title":".minimal"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit Pro also unlocks other more expressive themes, which provide their own unique visual baseline:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"tabs":[{"title":".aesthetic","content":[{"type":"row","columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"aesthetic-boho","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[]}],"numberOfColumns":3}]},{"title":".candyShop","content":[{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"candyshop"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"candyshop-cuppycake","type":"image"}]}],"size":1},{"content":[],"size":1}],"numberOfColumns":3,"type":"row"}]},{"title":".colorful","content":[{"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"colorful-blue"}]}],"size":1},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"colorful-green","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"colorful-orange"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"row","numberOfColumns":3}]},{"title":".neon","content":[{"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"neon"}]}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[]},{"content":[],"size":1}],"numberOfColumns":3,"type":"row"}]},{"title":".tron","content":[{"numberOfColumns":3,"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"tron"}]}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"tron-fcon"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"tron-virus","type":"image"}]}]}],"type":"row"}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can get a list of all predefined themes, as well as all pre-defined style variations, using the static ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/allPredefined","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" properties. You can create your own themes, as well as custom style variations for all predefined themes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Views","text":"Views"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit Pro unlocks views in the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" namespace, that make it easy to preview and present keyboard themes:"}]},{"tabs":[{"title":"Shelf","content":[{"type":"row","columns":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"themeshelf"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"size":1},{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A keyboard theme ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/Shelf","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be used to list themes in a vertical list of horizontally scrolling shelves."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can use the standard ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/ShelfItem"},{"type":"text","text":" to show how a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Keyboard\/Button"},{"type":"text","text":" will look, or use completely custom views for the titles and items."}]}]}],"numberOfColumns":2}]}],"type":"tabNavigator"},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"How-to","text":"How to…"},{"text":"…create a custom theme","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"create-a-custom-theme"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Since a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is just a struct, you can easily create your own custom themes by just defining new static theme value types."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For instance, this theme only changes the color of the primary button:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["extension KeyboardTheme {","","    static var greenPrimary: Self {","        get throws {","            try? Self(primaryBackgroundColor: .green)","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can also use other themes as a base when creating your own custom themes, if you only want to change a small part of a theme.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For instance, this theme starts with the minimal theme and changes the color of the primary button to pink:"}]},{"code":["extension KeyboardTheme {","","    static var pinkPrimary: Self {","        get throws {","            var theme = try? KeyboardTheme.minimal","            theme.buttonStyles[.primary]?.backgroundColor = .green","            return theme","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can also create custom themes that just tweak a style variation of another theme.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For instance, this custom theme is a standard theme that applies a black tint color style variation:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["extension KeyboardTheme {","","    static var standardBlack: Self {","        .standard(.init(tint: .black))","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All these combinations make the theme engine very flexible and powerful."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/keyboardkitpro\/themes-article"]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/keyboardkitpro\/themes-article"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Themes-Article","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"This article describes the KeyboardKit Pro theme engine.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Essentials-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Actions-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/AI-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/App-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Autocomplete-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Callouts-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Device-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Dictation-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Emojis-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/External-Keyboards-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Feedback-Article","doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/Ke